trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> types to UI Automation.
The element associated with this automation peer.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" /> class.

Gets the accelerator key for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.
Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAcceleratorKey" />.
A string that contains the accelerator key.

Gets the accelerator key combinations for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.

The accelerator key combinations for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.
Gets the class name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.
This method is called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName" />.
The class name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.

Gets the text that describes the functionality of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> control that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.
This method is called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetHelpText" />.

The text that describes the functionality of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> control that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.
Gets the name that describes the element that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.
This method is called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetName" />.
The name that describes the element that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.
A value enumeration that specifies the control pattern.

Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.

An object that supports the control pattern if <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is the <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Invoke" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Scroll" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Text" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SynchronizedInput" />, or <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Value" /> value; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.

Sends a request to activate the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonTextBox" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer" />.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
trans-unit.target: Ce membre est une implémentation d'un membre d'interface explicite.

trans-unit.source: It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IInvokeProvider> interface.
trans-unit.target: Il peut être utilisé uniquement lorsqu'un cast de l'instance de <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.RibbonTextBoxAutomationPeer> est effectué en une interface <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IInvokeProvider>.
